        <p>The biggest mistake: taking excessive risks to meet volume requirements quickly. The bonus isn't worth blowing your account. Trade your normal strategy with appropriate risk management. Meeting requirements over 60 days at 1% risk per trade is infinitely better than meeting them in 3 days with 10% risk per trade and losing everything.</p>

