        <h5>Eligible Instruments</h5>
        <p>Not all trades may count toward volume requirements. Some brokers exclude crypto or CFDs from bonus requirements, or weight them differently. A crypto trade might count at 50% while forex counts at 100%. Check which instruments contribute to meeting your bonus terms.</p>

